      "writtenOn": "2021-01-23T15:52:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "re seconds: yes, those protos are designed for humans to author them in text proto. Also that field was strongly-inspired by swarming.\nBuild.proto uses Duration (this field is copied from there): https://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/master/buildbucket/proto/build.proto#240\nand it was an attempt to find a better name.\n\n+1 to mention how this field interacts with the one in builder config, i.e. let\u0027s not just copy comment from build.proto as is. At the very least let\u0027s refer to Build.scheduling_timeout, instead of copying build.proto-specific stuff like status_details.",
